Manterror/Injector/Bumblebee:



Manterror got up slowly, shots from Ramulus sending him flying through the 
air backwards, smashing into a boulder, rolling over it and landing behind it.

---

Injector fired two stinger missiles at Ramulus' torso.

---

Bumblebee smiled, firing an optic blast at Dark Mouse, firing two stinger 
missiles from each launcher (four in all) at the tree Striker was hiding 
behind.
